snippet.title: Holy Potatoes! A Spy Story?! Teaser Trailer
snippet.description: Holy Potatoes! A Spy Story?! is a wacky spy-agency simulation game where you manage your very own spud spy headquarters! Recruit new spies, train and enhance your potato team, discover and build crazy gadgets, vehicles and facilities, and embark on top-secret missions!
